{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Self-Attention 从手撕开始\n",
    "\n",
    "本文档从零实现 Transformer 的核心 —— Self-Attention 机制。\n",
    "不使用任何深度学习框架的 Attention 封装，只依赖 NumPy 做矩阵运算，\n",
    "逐步拆解每一步的数学和代码。\n",
    "\n",
    "## 公式回顾\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\text{Attention}(Q, K, V) = \\text{softmax}\\left(\\frac{QK^T}{\\sqrt{d_k}}\\right)V\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "其中：\n",
    "- $Q \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n \\times d_{model}}$ — query 矩阵\n",
    "- $K \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n \\times d_{model}}$ — key 矩阵\n",
    "- $V \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n \\times d_{model}}$ — value 矩阵\n",
    "- $d_k$ — key 的维度\n",
    "- $n$ — 序列长度\n",
    "\n",
    "**核心直觉：**\n",
    "- Query 是\"问题向量\"，Key 是\"索引向量\"，Value 是\"内容向量\"\n",
    "- $QK^T$ 计算每对 token 之间的相关性（相似度）\n",
    "- Softmax 归一化得到注意力权重（每行和为 1）\n",
    "- 用权重加权求和 Value，得到每个位置的上下文表示"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "# 固定随机种子，保证可复现\n",
    "np.random.seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"NumPy version:\", np.__version__)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 第一步：构造示例数据\n",
    "\n",
    "假设我们有一个长度为 4 的句子，每个词用 6 维向量表示：\n",
    "- 序列长度 $n = 4$\n",
    "- 嵌入维度 $d_{model} = 6$\n",
    "- 头数 $h = 3$（每个头的维度 $d_k = d_{model} / h = 2$）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ---- 超参数 ----\n",
    "seq_len = 4       # 序列长度\n",
    "d_model = 6       # 模型维度\n",
    "num_heads = 3     # 头数\n",
    "d_k = d_model // num_heads  # 每个头的维度\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"序列长度: {seq_len}\")\n",
    "print(f\"模型维度: {d_model}\")\n",
    "print(f\"头数: {num_heads}\")\n",
    "print(f\"每个头的维度: {d_k}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 模拟一个批次的输入 (batch_size=1, seq_len=4, d_model=6)\n",
    "# 实际中这是 embedding + position encoding 之后的结果\n",
    "X = np.random.randn(1, seq_len, d_model)\n",
    "print(f\"\\n输入形状: {X.shape}\")\n",
    "print(\"输入张量:\\n\", X[0])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 第二步：线性投影生成 Q、K、V\n",
    "\n",
    "Self-Attention 的第一步是用三个不同的可学习线性变换把输入 $X$ 映射到 Q、K、V 空间：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "Q = XW_Q, \\quad K = XW_K, \\quad V = XW_V\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "其中 $W_Q, W_K, W_V \\in \\mathbb{R}^{d_{model} \\times d_{model}}$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def linear_projection(X, W):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    线性投影: X @ W\n",
    "    \n",
    "    Args:\n",
    "        X: (batch, seq_len, d_model) 输入\n",
    "        W: (d_model, d_model) 权重矩阵\n",
    "    Returns:\n",
    "        (batch, seq_len, d_model) 投影结果\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    return X @ W\n",
    "\n",
    "# 初始化三个权重矩阵（实际训练中这些是可学习的参数）\n",
    "W_Q = np.random.randn(d_model, d_model)\n",
    "W_K = np.random.randn(d_model, d_model)\n",
    "W_V = np.random.randn(d_model, d_model)\n",
    "\n",
    "Q = linear_projection(X, W_Q)\n",
    "K = linear_projection(X, W_K)\n",
    "V = linear_projection(X, W_V)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"Q 形状: {Q.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"K 形状: {K.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"V 形状: {V.shape}\")\n",
    "print(\"\\nQ[0]:\\n\", Q[0])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 第三步：缩放点积注意力 (Scaled Dot-Product Attention)\n",
    "\n",
    "这是 Self-Attention 的核心计算："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def scaled_dot_product_attention(Q, K, V, dropout_mask=None):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    缩放点积注意力\n",
    "    \n",
    "    Args:\n",
    "        Q: (batch, seq_len, d_model) 查询\n",
    "        K: (batch, seq_len, d_model) 键\n",
    "        V: (batch, seq_len, d_model) 值\n",
    "        dropout_mask: (batch, seq_len, seq_len) 可选的 dropout 掩码\n",
    "    Returns:\n",
    "        attn_output: (batch, seq_len, d_model)\n",
    "        attention_weights: (batch, seq_len, seq_len) softmax 后的权重\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    batch_size = Q.shape[0]\n",
    "    seq_len_q = Q.shape[1]\n",
    "    seq_len_k = K.shape[1]\n",
    "    d_k = Q.shape[-1]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 1: Q @ K^T -> (batch, seq_len_q, seq_len_k)\n",
    "    # 每一行 q_i 与每一行 k_j 做点积，衡量相关性\n",
    "    scores = np.matmul(Q, K.transpose(0, 2, 1))\n",
    "    print(f\"Step 1 - QK^T 形状: {scores.shape}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"  未缩放的注意力分数 (batch 0):\\n{scores[0]}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 2: 除以 sqrt(d_k)，防止梯度消失\n",
    "    # 当 d_k 很大时，点积结果的方差会变大，softmax 会变得很尖锐，\n",
    "    # 导致梯度接近 0。除以 sqrt(d_k) 将方差标准化到 1。\n",
    "    scaled_scores = scores / np.sqrt(d_k)\n",
    "    print(f\"\\nStep 2 - 缩放后形状: {scaled_scores.shape}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 3: Softmax 沿最后一个维度（列方向），使每行的注意力权重和为 1\n",
    "    # Softmax 数值稳定技巧：减去最大值\n",
    "    exp_scores = np.exp(scaled_scores - np.max(scaled_scores, axis=-1, keepdims=True))\n",
    "    attn_weights = exp_scores / np.sum(exp_scores, axis=-1, keepdims=True)\n",
    "    print(f\"\\nStep 3 - 注意力权重形状: {attn_weights.shape}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"  注意力权重 (batch 0):\\n{attn_weights[0]}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"  每行之和: {attn_weights[0].sum(axis=-1)}\")  # 应该全为 1.0\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 4: Dropout（训练时）\n",
    "    if dropout_mask is not None:\n",
    "        attn_weights = attn_weights * dropout_mask\n",
    "        # 重新归一化\n",
    "        attn_weights = attn_weights / np.sum(attn_weights, axis=-1, keepdims=True)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 5: 加权求和 Value\n",
    "    attn_output = np.matmul(attn_weights, V)\n",
    "    print(f\"\\nStep 4 - 输出形状: {attn_output.shape}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return attn_output, attn_weights\n",
    "\n",
    "attn_output, attn_weights = scaled_dot_product_attention(Q, K, V)\n",
    "print(f\"\\n最终输出 (batch 0):\\n{attn_output[0]}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 第四步：多头注意力 (Multi-Head Attention)\n",
    "\n",
    "多头注意力的核心思想是：把高维空间拆成多个低维\"子空间\"（头），\n",
    "每个头独立学习不同的表示子空间，最后拼接起来。\n",
    "\n",
    "流程：\n",
    "1. 把 Q、K、V 按最后一维切成 $h$ 个头\n",
    "2. 每个头独立做 Scaled Dot-Product Attention\n",
    "3. 把 $h$ 个头的输出拼接起来\n",
    "4. 做一次最终的线性变换 $W^O$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def split_heads(x, num_heads):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    将 (batch, seq_len, d_model) 重塑为 (batch, num_heads, seq_len, d_k)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    操作：先 split 再 transpose\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    batch, seq_len, d_model = x.shape\n",
    "    d_k = d_model // num_heads\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # (batch, seq_len, num_heads, d_k) -> (batch, num_heads, seq_len, d_k)\n",
    "    x = x.reshape(batch, seq_len, num_heads, d_k)\n",
    "    return x.transpose(0, 2, 1, 3)\n",
    "\n",
    "def merge_heads(x, num_heads):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    将 (batch, num_heads, seq_len, d_k) 重塑回 (batch, seq_len, d_model)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    操作：先 transpose 再 reshape\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    batch, num_heads, seq_len, d_k = x.shape\n",
    "    d_model = num_heads * d_k\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # (batch, num_heads, seq_len, d_k) -> (batch, seq_len, num_heads, d_k)\n",
    "    x = x.transpose(0, 2, 1, 3)\n",
    "    return x.reshape(batch, seq_len, d_model)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 验证 reshape 的正确性\n",
    "Q_heads = split_heads(Q, num_heads)\n",
    "K_heads = split_heads(K, num_heads)\n",
    "V_heads = split_heads(V, num_heads)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"Q_heads 形状: {Q_heads.shape}\")  # (1, 3, 4, 2)\n",
    "print(f\"K_heads 形状: {K_heads.shape}\")  # (1, 3, 4, 2)\n",
    "print(f\"V_heads 形状: {V_heads.shape}\")  # (1, 3, 4, 2)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 验证合并回去是否一致\n",
    "merged = merge_heads(Q_heads, num_heads)\n",
    "assert np.allclose(merged, Q), \"Split-Merge 不一致！\"\n",
    "print(\"\\n✓ Split-Merge 一致性检查通过\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def multi_head_attention(X, num_heads, W_Q, W_K, W_V, W_O, dropout_mask=None):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    完整的多头注意力前向传播\n",
    "    \n",
    "    Args:\n",
    "        X: (batch, seq_len, d_model) 输入\n",
    "        num_heads: 头数\n",
    "        W_Q, W_K, W_V: (d_model, d_model) 投影权重\n",
    "        W_O: (d_model, d_model) 输出投影权重\n",
    "        dropout_mask: 可选的 dropout 掩码\n",
    "    Returns:\n",
    "        output: (batch, seq_len, d_model)\n",
    "        attn_weights: (batch, num_heads, seq_len, seq_len) 所有头的注意力权重\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    batch_size = X.shape[0]\n",
    "    d_model = X.shape[-1]\n",
    "    d_k = d_model // num_heads\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 1: 线性投影\n",
    "    Q = X @ W_Q\n",
    "    K = X @ W_K\n",
    "    V = X @ W_V\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 2: 拆分多头\n",
    "    Q_heads = split_heads(Q, num_heads)      # (batch, num_heads, seq_len, d_k)\n",
    "    K_heads = split_heads(K, num_heads)\n",
    "    V_heads = split_heads(V, num_heads)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 3: 每个头独立做 attention\n",
    "    # 这里利用广播机制，一次处理所有头\n",
    "    # scores: (batch, num_heads, seq_len, seq_len)\n",
    "    scores = np.matmul(Q_heads, K_heads.transpose(0, 1, 3, 2)) / np.sqrt(d_k)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Softmax\n",
    "    exp_scores = np.exp(scores - np.max(scores, axis=-1, keepdims=True))\n",
    "    attn_weights_per_head = exp_scores / np.sum(exp_scores, axis=-1, keepdims=True)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Dropout\n",
    "    if dropout_mask is not None:\n",
    "        attn_weights_per_head = attn_weights_per_head * dropout_mask\n",
    "        attn_weights_per_head = attn_weights_per_head / np.sum(\n",
    "            attn_weights_per_head, axis=-1, keepdims=True\n",
    "        )\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Weighted sum\n",
    "    attn_output_per_head = np.matmul(attn_weights_per_head, V_heads)  # (batch, num_heads, seq_len, d_k)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 4: 拼接所有头\n",
    "    concat_output = merge_heads(attn_output_per_head, num_heads)  # (batch, seq_len, d_model)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 5: 最终线性变换\n",
    "    output = concat_output @ W_O\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return output, attn_weights_per_head\n",
    "\n",
    "# 初始化 W_O\n",
    "W_O = np.random.randn(d_model, d_model)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 运行多头注意力\n",
    "mha_output, mha_weights = multi_head_attention(X, num_heads, W_Q, W_K, W_V, W_O)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"多头注意力输出形状: {mha_output.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"注意力权重形状: {mha_weights.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"\\n输出 (batch 0):\\n{mha_output[0]}\")\n",
    "print(f\"\\n注意力权重 (head 0):\\n{mha_weights[0, 0]}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 第五步：可视化注意力权重\n",
    "\n",
    "让我们看看模型实际学到了什么样的注意力模式。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 可视化注意力权重热力图\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, num_heads, figsize=(5 * num_heads, 4))\n",
    "\n",
    "words = [\"我\", \"爱\", \"吃\", \"猫\"]  # 模拟一个中文句子\n",
    "\n",
    "for i in range(num_heads):\n",
    "    ax = axes[i] if num_heads > 1 else axes\n",
    "    heatmap = ax.matshow(mha_weights[0, i], cmap='Blues', vmin=0, vmax=1)\n",
    "    ax.set_xticks(range(seq_len))\n",
    "    ax.set_yticks(range(seq_len))\n",
    "    ax.set_xticklabels(words, fontsize=10)\n",
    "    ax.set_yticklabels(words, fontsize=10)\n",
    "    ax.set_xlabel('Key token', fontsize=11)\n",
    "    ax.set_ylabel('Query token', fontsize=11)\n",
    "    ax.set_title(f'Head {i}', fontsize=12)\n",
    "    fig.colorbar(heatmap, ax=ax)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 在每个格子里写上数值\n",
    "    for j in range(seq_len):\n",
    "        for k in range(seq_len):\n",
    "            ax.text(k, j, f'{mha_weights[0, i, j, k]:.2f}', \n",
    "                    ha='center', va='center', fontsize=8,\n",
    "                    color='white' if mha_weights[0, i, j, k] > 0.5 else 'black')\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.suptitle('Multi-Head Attention Weights Visualization', fontsize=14, y=1.02)\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.savefig('attention_heatmap.png', dpi=150, bbox_inches='tight')\n",
    "print(\"✓ 热力图已保存为 attention_heatmap.png\")\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 第六步：对比 PyTorch 验证正确性\n",
    "\n",
    "用 PyTorch 的官方实现验证我们的手写版本是否正确。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "try:\n",
    "    import torch\n",
    "    import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(\"PyTorch version:\", torch.__version__)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 用相同的权重\n",
    "    torch_X = torch.tensor(X, dtype=torch.float32)\n",
    "    torch_W_Q = torch.tensor(W_Q, dtype=torch.float32)\n",
    "    torch_W_K = torch.tensor(W_K, dtype=torch.float32)\n",
    "    torch_W_V = torch.tensor(W_V, dtype=torch.float32)\n",
    "    torch_W_O = torch.tensor(W_O, dtype=torch.float32)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 使用 PyTorch 的 MultiheadAttention\n",
    "    batch_size = 1\n",
    "    mha_torch = nn.MultiheadAttention(\n",
    "        embed_dim=d_model,\n",
    "        num_heads=num_heads,\n",
    "        batch_first=True,\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 手动设置权重\n",
    "    with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "        mha_torch.in_proj_weight.copy_(torch.cat([torch_W_Q, torch_W_K, torch_W_V]))\n",
    "        mha_torch.out_proj.weight.copy_(torch_W_O)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 前向传播\n",
    "    torch_output, _ = mha_torch(torch_X, torch_X, torch_X)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 对比结果\n",
    "    diff = np.abs(mha_output - torch_output.numpy()).max()\n",
    "    print(f\"\\nNumPy 实现 vs PyTorch 实现的最大差异: {diff:.6e}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if diff < 1e-5:\n",
    "        print(\"✓ 两者结果一致！我们的实现是正确的。\")\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        print(\"⚠ 存在差异，可能需要检查实现细节。\")\n",
    "        print(f\"\\nNumPy 输出:\\n{mha_output[0]}\")\n",
    "        print(f\"\\nPyTorch 输出:\\n{torch_output[0].numpy()}\")\n",
    "        \n",
    "except ImportError:\n",
    "    print(\"PyTorch 未安装，跳过验证步骤。\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 第七步：反向传播（手动推导梯度）\n",
    "\n",
    "Self-Attention 的反向传播是理解自动微分原理的好材料。\n",
    "我们手动推导每个步骤的梯度。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def scaled_dot_product_attention_backward(d_output, Q, K, V, attn_weights, d_k):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    Scaled Dot-Product Attention 的反向传播\n",
    "    \n",
    "    计算 dQ, dK, dV\n",
    "    \n",
    "    前向: attn = softmax(QK^T / sqrt(d_k)) @ V\n",
    "    \n",
    "    梯度推导:\n",
    "    1. dV = attn_weights^T @ d_output\n",
    "    2. d_attn = d_output @ V^T\n",
    "    3. d_scores = softmax_deriv(attn_weights) @ d_attn\n",
    "    4. d_QK = d_scores * (1/sqrt(d_k))\n",
    "    5. dQ = d_QK @ K, dK = d_QK^T @ Q\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    batch_size, seq_len, d_model = d_output.shape\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 1: dV\n",
    "    # attn_output = attn_weights @ V\n",
    "    dV = attn_weights.transpose(0, 1, 3, 2) @ d_output  # (batch, num_heads, seq_len, d_k)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 2: d_attn (softmax 之前的加权梯度)\n",
    "    d_attn = d_output @ V.transpose(0, 2, 1)  # (batch, seq_len, seq_len)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 3: softmax 导数\n",
    "    # softmax'(z)_ij = a_i * (delta_ij - delta_ij * a_j)\n",
    "    # 等价于: d_scores = a * (d_attn - sum(d_attn * a, keepdim=True))\n",
    "    d_scaled_scores = attn_weights * (d_attn - np.sum(d_attn * attn_weights, axis=-1, keepdims=True))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 4: 缩放逆操作\n",
    "    d_QK = d_scaled_scores * (1.0 / np.sqrt(d_k))  # (batch, seq_len, seq_len)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Step 5: Q @ K^T 的梯度\n",
    "    # dQ = d_QK @ K, dK = d_QK^T @ Q\n",
    "    dQ = d_QK @ K.transpose(0, 2, 1)\n",
    "    dK = d_QK.transpose(0, 2, 1) @ Q\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return dQ, dK, dV\n",
    "\n",
    "# 构造一个虚拟的损失梯度来测试反向传播\n",
    "d_loss = np.ones_like(mha_output)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 由于 multi_head_attention 内部做了 reshape，需要调整 d_loss 的形状\n",
    "# 这里简化演示 single-head 的反向传播\n",
    "dQ_single, dK_single, dV_single = scaled_dot_product_attention_backward(\n",
    "    d_loss, Q, K, V, attn_weights, d_k\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"dQ 形状: {dQ_single.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"dK 形状: {dK_single.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"dV 形状: {dV_single.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"\\ndQ 范数: {np.linalg.norm(dQ_single):.4f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"dK 范数: {np.linalg.norm(dK_single):.4f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"dV 范数: {np.linalg.norm(dV_single):.4f}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 对比 PyTorch autograd 验证梯度\n",
    "try:\n",
    "    import torch\n",
    "    import torch.nn.functional as F\n",
    "    \n",
    "    t_Q = torch.tensor(Q[0], requires_grad=True, dtype=torch.float32)\n",
    "    t_K = torch.tensor(K[0], requires_grad=True, dtype=torch.float32)\n",
    "    t_V = torch.tensor(V[0], requires_grad=True, dtype=torch.float32)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    t_scores = torch.matmul(t_Q, t_K.transpose(0, 1)) / np.sqrt(d_k)\n",
    "    t_attn = F.softmax(t_scores, dim=-1)\n",
    "    t_output = torch.matmul(t_attn, t_V)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 反向传播\n",
    "    t_loss = torch.ones_like(t_output)\n",
    "    t_output.backward(t_loss)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    torch_dQ = t_Q.grad.numpy()\n",
    "    torch_dK = t_K.grad.numpy()\n",
    "    torch_dV = t_V.grad.numpy()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(f\"\\n=== 单头反向传播梯度验证 ===\")\n",
    "    print(f\"dQ 最大差异: {np.abs(dQ_single[0] - torch_dQ).max():.6e}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"dK 最大差异: {np.abs(dK_single[0] - torch_dK).max():.6e}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"dV 最大差异: {np.abs(dV_single[0] - torch_dV).max():.6e}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if (np.abs(dQ_single[0] - torch_dQ).max() < 1e-5 and\n",
    "        np.abs(dK_single[0] - torch_dK).max() < 1e-5 and\n",
    "        np.abs(dV_single[0] - torch_dV).max() < 1e-5):\n",
    "        print(\"✓ 反向传播梯度验证通过！\")\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        print(\"⚠ 梯度存在差异\")\n",
    "        \n",
    "except ImportError:\n",
    "    print(\"PyTorch 未安装，跳过梯度验证。\")"
   ]
